    },
    {
      "start": 528.25,
      "end": 529.75,
      "text": "So just wait"
    },
    {
      "start": 529.75,
      "end": 530.35,
      "text": "until Monday"
    },
    {
      "start": 530.35,
      "end": 531.21,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 531.21,
      "end": 533.43,
      "text": "But in the meantime"
    },
    {
      "start": 533.43,
      "end": 534.31,
      "text": "Oh ho"
    },
    {
      "start": 534.31,
      "end": 535.15,
      "text": "she has an idea"
    },
    {
      "start": 535.15,
      "end": 535.49,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 535.49,
      "end": 536.87,
      "text": "But in the meantime"
    },
    {
      "start": 536.87,
      "end": 538.37,
      "text": "come to the wedding"
    },
    {
      "start": 538.37,
      "end": 539.31,
      "text": "Wow"
    },
    {
      "start": 539.31,
      "end": 539.91,
      "text": "Wow"
    },
    {
      "start": 539.91,
      "end": 540.73,
      "text": "그동안에"
    },
    {
      "start": 540.73,
      "end": 541.95,
      "text": "But in the meantime"
    },
    {
      "start": 541.95,
      "end": 543.13,
      "text": "대체한다면"
    },
    {
      "start": 543.13,
      "end": 543.71,
      "text": "meanwhile"
    },
    {
      "start": 543.71,
      "end": 545.27,
      "text": "이렇게 대체할 수도 있겠죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 545.27,
      "end": 546.63,
      "text": "Come to the wedding"
    },
    {
      "start": 546.63,
      "end": 547.77,
      "text": "결혼식에"
    },
    {
      "start": 547.77,
      "end": 548.95,
      "text": "참석해 주세요"
    },
    {
      "start": 548.95,
      "end": 549.95,
      "text": "라는 표현입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 549.95,
      "end": 551.35,
      "text": "We can get to know"
    },
    {
      "start": 551.35,
      "end": 552.63,
      "text": "each other better"
    },
    {
      "start": 552.63,
      "end": 554.43,
      "text": "Do they need to know"
    },
    {
      "start": 554.43,
      "end": 555.17,
      "text": "each other better?"
    },
    {
      "start": 555.39,
      "end": 556.35,
      "text": "I don't think so"
    },
    {
      "start": 556.35,
      "end": 558.07,
      "text": "They're business partners"
    },
    {
      "start": 558.07,
      "end": 559.77,
      "text": "potential business partners"
    },
    {
      "start": 559.77,
      "end": 561.71,
      "text": "지금 경영장부라든지"
    },
    {
      "start": 561.71,
      "end": 562.61,
      "text": "아니면 인도의"
    },
    {
      "start": 562.61,
      "end": 563.99,
      "text": "아동 실태에 대해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 563.99,
      "end": 565.01,
      "text": "좀 객관적인"
    },
    {
      "start": 565.01,
      "end": 566.61,
      "text": "리포트를"
    },
    {
      "start": 566.61,
      "end": 567.65,
      "text": "더 잘"
    },
    {
      "start": 567.65,
      "end": 568.89,
      "text": "보고를 받아야 되는"
    },
    {
      "start": 568.89,
      "end": 569.63,
      "text": "상황일 텐데"
    },
    {
      "start": 569.63,
      "end": 571.29,
      "text": "서로에 대해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 571.29,
      "end": 573.07,
      "text": "더 잘 알아야 된다는"
    },
    {
      "start": 573.07,
      "end": 573.59,
      "text": "이야기네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 573.59,
      "end": 574.15,
      "text": "Personally"
    },
    {
      "start": 574.15,
      "end": 574.59,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 574.59,
      "end": 575.79,
      "text": "They can do business"
    },
    {
      "start": 575.79,
      "end": 576.81,
      "text": "over a cup of coffee"
    },
    {
      "start": 576.81,
      "end": 577.93,
      "text": "in the office"
    },
    {
      "start": 577.93,
      "end": 578.91,
      "text": "at a restaurant"
    },
    {
      "start": 578.91,
      "end": 580.03,
      "text": "It's easy, right?"
    },
    {
      "start": 580.49,
      "end": 581.73,
      "text": "But what can they do"
    },
    {
      "start": 581.73,
      "end": 583.03,
      "text": "at her daughter's wedding?"
    },
    {
      "start": 583.73,
      "end": 584.65,
      "text": "What can they do there?"
    },
    {
      "start": 585.03,
      "end": 585.87,
      "text": "그러니까요"
    },
    {
      "start": 585.87,
      "end": 587.01,
      "text": "자 계속해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 587.01,
      "end": 588.29,
      "text": "이자벨이 뭐라고"
    },
    {
      "start": 588.29,
      "end": 589.17,
      "text": "대답을 하는지"
    },
    {
      "start": 589.17,
      "end": 589.83,
      "text": "들어보겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 589.83,
      "end": 592.13,
      "text": "I have a flight to India?"
    },
    {
      "start": 592.45,
      "end": 593.67,
      "text": "당연한 반응이죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 593.67,
      "end": 595.13,
      "text": "I have a flight to India"
    },
    {
      "start": 595.13,
      "end": 597.59,
      "text": "저는 인도로 가는"
    },
    {
      "start": 597.59,
      "end": 598.79,
      "text": "비행기를 타야 해요"
    },
    {
      "start": 598.79,
      "end": 600.03,
      "text": "라는 의미가 되겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 600.03,
      "end": 601.87,
      "text": "She really wants to get on that flight"
    },
    {
      "start": 601.87,
      "end": 602.83,
      "text": "ASAP"
    },
    {
      "start": 602.83,
      "end": 605.11,
      "text": "She also had a special plan"
    },
    {
      "start": 605.11,
      "end": 607.01,
      "text": "for a little child"
    },
    {
      "start": 607.01,
      "end": 607.61,
      "text": "그쵸?"
    },
    {
      "start": 607.67,
      "end": 609.19,
      "text": "Yeah, the kid that she has raised"
    },
    {
      "start": 609.19,
      "end": 610.91,
      "text": "since he was one years old"
    },
    {
      "start": 610.91,
      "end": 612.47,
      "text": "The little cute boy"
    },
    {
      "start": 612.47,
      "end": 613.73,
      "text": "who is so cute in this movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 613.73,
      "end": 615.15,
      "text": "아주 아주 귀여운 인도"
    },
    {
      "start": 615.15,
      "end": 617.01,
      "text": "꼬마 소년이 있었는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 617.01,
      "end": 619.17,
      "text": "그 아이의 birthday가 있었어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 619.17,
      "end": 620.77,
      "text": "그래서 그 날에 맞춰서"
    },
    {
      "start": 620.77,
      "end": 622.79,
      "text": "꼭 인도로 돌아가려고 했죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 622.79,
      "end": 624.25,
      "text": "Well, you know"
    },
    {
      "start": 624.25,
      "end": 625.59,
      "text": "Staying the weekend"
    },
    {
      "start": 625.59,
      "end": 626.97,
      "text": "won't kill you"
    },
    {
      "start": 626.97,
      "end": 628.87,
      "text": "아주 쉽게 이야기하네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 628.87,
      "end": 630.13,
      "text": "Well, you know"
    },
    {
      "start": 630.13,
      "end": 631.11,
      "text": "Staying the weekend"
    },
    {
      "start": 631.11,
      "end": 632.11,
      "text": "won't kill you"
    },
    {
      "start": 632.11,
      "end": 633.49,
      "text": "해석되시죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 633.85,
      "end": 635.25,
      "text": "Staying the weekend"
    },
    {
      "start": 635.25,
      "end": 637.07,
      "text": "won't kill you"
    },
    {
      "start": 637.07,
      "end": 639.52,
      "text": "똑같이 표현하지 않나요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 639.72,
      "end": 640.24,
      "text": "우리말로도"
    },
    {
      "start": 640.24,
      "end": 640.74,
      "text": "In Korean?"
    },
    {
      "start": 640.9,
      "end": 641.96,
      "text": "How do you say it in Korean?"
    },
    {
      "start": 641.96,
      "end": 642.88,
      "text": "그러니까 뭐"
    },
    {
      "start": 642.88,
      "end": 645.68,
      "text": "주말 동안 머문다고 해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 645.68,
      "end": 647.6,
      "text": "그게 너를 어떻게 잡아먹지 않아"
    },
    {
      "start": 647.6,
      "end": 648.38,
      "text": "이런 말 있잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 648.38,
      "end": 650.14,
      "text": "It's fine"
    },
    {
      "start": 650.14,
      "end": 652.14,
      "text": "무슨 큰일이 나는 건 아니잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 652.14,
      "end": 653.42,
      "text": "라는 의미가 되겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 653.42,
      "end": 654.52,
      "text": "No problem"
    },
    {
      "start": 654.52,
      "end": 655.36,
      "text": "Relax"
    },
    {
      "start": 655.36,
      "end": 656.72,
      "text": "그러니까 지금"
    },
    {
      "start": 656.72,
      "end": 658.02,
      "text": "테레사는 계속해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 658.02,
      "end": 659.38,
      "text": "Just kept trying to hold"
    },
    {
      "start": 659.38,
      "end": 660.3,
      "text": "이자벨"
    },
    {
      "start": 660.3,
      "end": 660.72,
      "text": "그쵸?"
    },
    {
      "start": 661.1,
      "end": 662.58,
      "text": "Yeah, don't go"
    },
    {
      "start": 662.58,
      "end": 663.68,
      "text": "Whatever you do"
    },
    {
      "start": 663.68,
      "end": 665.42,
      "text": "You need to stay in New York"
    },
    {
      "start": 665.42,
      "end": 667.4,
      "text": "She's not comfortable in New York"
    },
    {
      "start": 667.4,
      "end": 670.42,
      "text": "She's lived in India so long"
    },
    {
      "start": 670.42,
      "end": 673.36,
      "text": "That New York is like a foreign place to her"
    },
    {
      "start": 673.36,
      "end": 675.24,
      "text": "Even though she used to live there"
    },
    {
      "start": 675.24,
      "end": 676.52,
      "text": "Way back when"
    },
    {
      "start": 676.52,
      "end": 678.78,
      "text": "너무 오랫동안 인도에 머물다 보니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 678.78,
      "end": 680.36,
      "text": "문화적인 괴리감도 되려"
    },
    {
      "start": 680.36,
      "end": 681.6,
      "text": "느끼고 있는 것 같았어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 681.6,
      "end": 682.96,
      "text": "아무튼 이 장면"
    },
    {
      "start": 682.96,
      "end": 683.9,
      "text": "한 번 더 들어보겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 683.9,
      "end": 685.92,
      "text": "I just have"
    },
    {
      "start": 685.92,
      "end": 688.1,
      "text": "I have a big weekend ahead of me"
    },
    {
      "start": 688.1,
      "end": 689.7,
      "text": "So why don't you leave all this with me"
    },
    {
      "start": 689.7,
      "end": 690.74,
      "text": "And we'll have lunch on Monday"
    },
    {
      "start": 690.74,
      "end": 691.72,
      "text": "And I'll tell you what I can do"
    },
    {
      "start": 691.72,
      "end": 692.92,
      "text": "But in the meantime"
    },
    {
      "start": 692.92,
      "end": 694.12,
      "text": "Come to the wedding"
    },
    {
      "start": 694.12,
      "end": 695.32,
      "text": "We can get to know each other better"
    },
    {
      "start": 695.32,
      "end": 696.44,
      "text": "I have a flight to India"
    },
    {
      "start": 696.44,
      "end": 697.22,
      "text": "Well, you know"
    },
    {
      "start": 697.22,
      "end": 699.33,
      "text": "Staying the weekend won't kill you"
    },
    {
      "start": 699.33,
      "end": 701.35,
      "text": "조미선님께서"
    },
    {
      "start": 701.35,
      "end": 702.89,
      "text": "예습하고 들었더니"
    },
    {
      "start": 702.89,
      "end": 704.47,
      "text": "확실히 잘 들리네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 704.47,
      "end": 706.39,
      "text": "내일도 예습하고 와야겠네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 706.39,
      "end": 706.83,
      "text": "흐흐"
    },
    {
      "start": 706.83,
      "end": 707.71,
      "text": "하셨습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 707.71,
      "end": 708.55,
      "text": "Yes, 예습"
    },
    {
      "start": 708.55,
      "end": 710.05,
      "text": "The power of 예습"
    },
    {
      "start": 710.05,
      "end": 710.81,
      "text": "그러니까요"
    },
    {
      "start": 710.81,
      "end": 711.85,
      "text": "아, 들으셨죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 711.85,
      "end": 713.55,
      "text": "예습에는 파워가 있습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 713.55,
      "end": 714.85,
      "text": "강추합니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 714.85,
      "end": 716.45,
      "text": "네, 오늘 스크린 잉글리쉬는"
    },
    {
      "start": 716.45,
      "end": 717.61,
      "text": "여기서 마무리하겠습니다"
    }
  ]
}